<div id="main-content" class="main-content">
    <main class="main-primary">
        <div class="section">
            <div class="container">

                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/btbl">Braille and Talking Books</a></li>
                    <li>Purchase Cartridge</li>
                </ol>

                <h2 class="page-title">@ViewBag.PageTitle</h2>

                <div class="group">
                    <p>
                        For listening to downloaded NLS books on the Digital Talking Book Machine, we encourage you to purchase a cartridge similar to the ones you receive from us by mail.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        As part of your initial cartridge purchase you will need to also obtain a cable that will connect the cartridge to your computer via the USB port. 
                        You may order a cable from the cartridge vendor or <a href="/btbl/contact/">contact BTBL</a> for one. 
                        BTBL has been given a limited number of cables and will distribute them at no charge until supplies run out.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        NLS maintains an updated <a href="https://www.loc.gov/nls/enrollment-equipment/equipment-needed-for-nls-materials/cartridges-cables-for-bard/">list of vendors for purchasing blank cartridges</a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>

